武、卢靖姗主演，为什么不走院线？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "国内各大流媒体平台已于 4 月 17 日上午 10 点整，上线网播了投资高达 5 亿元的知名 IP 电影《寻龙诀·觅踪》，这钱都花哪了？ 该片原名《鬼吹灯之天星术》，导演是拍摄过《古墓丽影》、《敢死队 2》、《机械师》、《空中监狱》、《黑鹰坠落》（制片人）等大片的好莱坞大咖西蒙·韦斯特，张涵予、姜武、卢靖姗分别饰演摸金校尉胡八一、王凯旋和 Shirley 杨 ，这部早在 2019 年就拍完的特效大片，在经历了补拍等各种风波之后，最终还是无缘院线，改名后化身成网大与观众见面，这么大的投资阵容，为什么不走院线？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-0f0532d991bb7ac92dc6c9b9721a4be8_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "95 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2027812510628069389"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIyZHjg6bE6rQBEAMaCTExOTE1NDc1MSDxyv3OBjAAOMICQBByEzIwMjc4MTI1MTA2MjgwNjkzODl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1776653070.590833", "card_id": "Q_2029373655168160683", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 18}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "25-26 赛季英超第 33 轮 曼城 2-1 战胜阿森纳，如何评价本场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-4228aed21fdd9476816ad2b86a670c41_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "89 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2029373655168160683"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIyZHjg6bE6rQBEAMaCTExOTIwNjMyMiDfppTPBjAAOBNAEXITMjAyOTM3MzY1NTE2ODE2MDY4M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1776653070.591133", "card_id": "Q_2028941915911984616", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 72}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么沙特会愿意让巴基斯坦驻军自己国家，这不是不平等协议么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "4 月 11 日，根据沙特阿拉伯国防部的公开声明，巴基斯坦的中械师正式入驻沙特东部地区的阿卜杜勒阿齐兹国王空军基地，人数约 1.3 万人，以空军和防空装备为主，带有完整防空体系（拥有 LY-80 、 FM-90 等中国防空导弹），还有 10~18 架作战和支援飞机（含歼 - 10CE 、 JF-17 枭龙、 ZDK-03 预警机等中式装备）。 巴基斯坦表示此事属实，新华网也对此事做了报道。 沙特国防部声明，这是依据沙特和巴基斯坦两国签署的战略防务协议所实施的行动，巴基斯坦驻军将有助于维护地区和国际层面的安全与稳定。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f07b96822fa9f213b91a65a9512984d6_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2028941915911984616"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIyZHjg6bE6rQBEAMaCTExOTE5MzYwNSDIgo7PBjAAOJIBQBJyEzIwMjg5NDE5MTU5MTE5ODQ2MTZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1776653070.591749", "card_id": "Q_2029251695079682936", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 106}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价李雨桐泄露薛之谦手机号、身份证被行拘？法律上如何界定这类行为？这次处罚能终结两人近十年恩怨吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "4 月 19 日下午，北京广播电视台《法治进行时》栏目在官方账号发布多条视频。视频中，接受采访的薛之谦所属经纪公司潮石音乐工作人员提到，因在今年 3 月喊话薛之谦的微博中刻意泄露薛之谦手机号、身份证等个人信息，经公安机关调查情况属实，根据《中华人民共和国治安管理处罚法》第五十六条第一款规定，李雨桐被处以行政拘留十日的处罚，拘留日期为 2026 年 4 月 10 日至 2026 年 4 月 20 日。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b4e81aaa57cda70f42d7324cb3880426_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2029251695079682936"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIyZHjg6bE6rQBEAMaCTExOTIwMjY0MiDJw5LPBjAAOO8CQBNyEzIwMjkyNTE2OTUwNzk2ODI5MzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1776653070.592294", "card_id": "Q_2027410498283414838", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 17}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价博主曝光的苹果首款折叠屏 iPhone Fold 最终版设计？此时入局折叠屏领域还有优势吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有博主在社交平台上分享了苹果首款折叠屏 iPhone Fold 的外观，据称这是该产品的最终版设计方案。 iPhone Fold 采用了主流的书本式折叠方案，是一款阔折叠机型，其背部相机模组采用了独特的横置排列，配备两颗后置镜头，在设计语言上与以往的 iPhone 有着显著的区别。 该机的屏幕规格十分亮眼，外屏尺寸约为 5.3 英寸，展开后的内屏则达到了 7.7 英寸左右。这种尺寸布局让它在展开状态下几乎等同于一台 iPad mini，兼顾了便携与高效。 这款具有里程碑意义的新机预计将在今年秋季正式发布。届时，它将与 iPhone 18 Pro 系列同台亮相，共同开启苹果移动终端的新篇章。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-8a29cbbd53587f4ca2ba40e7aa20701e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "84 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2027410498283414838"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIyZHjg6bE6rQBEAMaCTExOTE0MDIyOCCK3vfOBjAAOCJAFHITMjAyNzQxMDQ5ODI4MzQxNDgzOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1776653070.593442", "card_id": "Q_2028371416911738495", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "3 岁的孩子能问 100 多个问题，而 11 岁后几乎为 0，这是为什么呢？我们的教育到底是怎么了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a356abbf3dc7b739e52503b1ae02f2ce_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "83 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2028371416911738495"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIyZHjg6bE6rQBEAMaCTExOTE3MjY0MCD324XPBjAAOEJAFXITMjAyODM3MTQxNjkxMTczODQ5NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1776653070.593783", "card_id": "Q_19341622405226751